cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.DS

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image registration of histological images. It could also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category as histological images are a type of medical imaging. Information retrieval (cs.IR) is another possible sub-category as the paper discusses a method for automatically aligning images. Machine learning (cs.LG) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) are also possible sub-categories as the paper mentions the use of a distance measure and a parametric registration method.
